---
title: Orange Sesame Prawn & Jasmine Rice with Cucumber Salad
description: Did someone say orange prawns? These sticky, sweet and sesame-coated pieces of golden juicy prawns are bringing back memories of takeaway meals from our childhood. And on the table in fifteen minutes? We don’t think it gets much better than that!

